me half to death.

01:13:59.849 --> 01:14:01.951
Where are you running off to?

01:14:01.984 --> 01:14:03.686
I was coming to find you.

01:14:05.888 --> 01:14:08.657
What are you doing here?

01:14:08.691 --> 01:14:10.026
